### Get today's activities
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/activities/today
Authorization: Bearer user_token_value_here

### Get all activities (Admin only)
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/activities/all
Authorization: Bearer admin_token_value_here

### Get my activities with date range
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/activities?startDate=2026-01-01&endDate=2026-01-02
Authorization: Bearer user_token_value_here

### Get activities by user (Admin only)
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/activities/user/695793ebcac261dff38180f5
Authorization: Bearer admin_token_value_here